      "content": "Understood. I'm seeing the thermal anomaly on my end too. I need to run a full diagnostic on that navigation processor to clear the error. I'm going to initiate a system-wide reset and a soft reboot of the core processing unit to see if that resolves the heat sink issue. Stand by for the command.",
